data.title: Marshall University
data.meta_description: Alex Zurbuch - 2011: Placed 141st at the NCAA Mid-Atlantic Regional with a 10k time of 34:03.6... Posted an 8k mark of 26:57.2 at the C-USA Championships... ...
data.text:
2011: Placed 141st at the NCAA Mid-Atlantic Regional with a 10k time of 34:03.6... Posted an 8k mark of 26:57.2 at the C-USA Championships... Finished fifth on the team at the EKU Relays with a 5k time of 16:06.00... C-USA Commissioner[apos]s Honor Roll.

2010: Ran a 15:32 5K at the EKU Invitational... Was 30th at the Old Timers Classic in a time of 27:50... Was 36th at the Evansville Invitational in his fastest time of 26:29... Also ran that time at the Conference USA Championship Meet, placing 44th overall.

2009: 17th at the Greensboro Invitational... 19th at EKU... Placed 22nd at the Furman Invitational... 49th at the C-USA Championships.

Prior to Marshall: Three-time all NCAC (2004-06-07)... 2007 NCAC Runner of the Year... Cross country All-State in 2006... Was a four year member of the All-Region Team (2004-07).
